@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_zikobu(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (v1 * tmp)
    v0 = wp.cos(0.94)
    tmp = (wp.sin(v0) * tmp)
    v0 = (0.45 + v0)
    v0 = tmp
    v1 = wp.abs(((v2 + 0.27 - v1 + 0.94) - (tmp + 0.20 * tmp + 0.60)))
    v2 = (wp.abs(wp.exp(v2 + 0.89)) + (wp.exp(v0 + 0.60) + 0.53))
    v2 = (v0 / wp.cos((v1 + 0.82 + tmp + 0.82)))
    data[tid] = v0
